The competition for grass mowing in road partitions shall be announced.
SJSC Latvian road maintainer has announced procurement for mechanized mowing of grass in the road partitions in Latvian regions and in Pierīga, informs LAU.
The subject of the procurement is divided into 9 lots: Aluksne, Daugavpils, Jēkabpils, Jelgava, Rēzekne, Valmiera, Talsi and Riga road districts.
Tenderers may submit a tender for one or more lots.
